parameters.text:
={{ $('AI Agent').item.json.output.prompts }} 

Extract each prompt individually in the format: 
'1. Title > Text', '2. Title > Text', and so on, based on the order of prompts in the input. 

Ensure the output matches this structure exactly: 'Number. Title > Text'. 

Remove any special characters like '*', '\', '"', or others from the title and text, and ensure no extra spaces or formatting issues. 

For example: '1. Platform Analysis > Identify top marketing channels for my business. What platforms vibe with my target audience and market trends?'

JSON example: 

{
    "prompts": [
      {
        "name": "1. Platform Analysis > Identify top marketing channels for my business. What platforms vibe with my target audience and market trends?"
      },
      {
        "name": "2. Content Strategy > Suggest a content plan for social media growth."
      },
      {
        "name": "3. Budget Planning > Estimate costs for a digital marketing campaign."
      },
      {
        "name": "4. Audience Targeting > Define my ideal customer profile based on demographics and behavior."
      },
      {
        "name": "5. Social Media Ads > Design a strategy for effective ad campaigns on Instagram and Facebook."
      },
      {
        "name": "6. SEO Optimization > Recommend keywords to improve my website's search engine ranking."
      },
      {
        "name": "7. Email Marketing > Create a plan for a successful email drip campaign."
      }
    ]
}

